name:
2-Tier Nautical
(Baby Neutral)
description:
A two tier diaper cake makes a beautiful and impressive centerpiece for a baby shower. Each cake is decorated with ribbons, baby products and a plush cake topper - perfect for every baby Approximately 10" high and 8" in diameter.

This one tier small diaper cake comes with the following ingredients:
-- 31 Size 1 Pampers Sensitive diapers 
-- 2 onesies
-- 2 wash cloths
-- 1 Plush cake topper
